-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Use 'create <name> <password>' to create a character.
Use 'connect <name> <password>' to connect to your existing character.
Use 'connect Guest' to connect to a Guest character.
Use 'WHO' to see who's currently online.
Use 'QUIT' to logout.
